modName: Leonidis - Half High Elf and Half Dremora
summary: This time I played a little bit with the settings and got a good looking High Elf / Dremora Hybrid!
descriptionHtml:
This guy is a Half Blood. half High Elf and Half Dremora.
This time he got lighter Skin, some Scars in the face and a light war painting around the eyes.

He will also have the Dremora Voice while fighting with enemys instead of the High Elf Voice.

Hope you like him, I think I will stick with him from now and play a little bit to see how the shouts will be with the dremora voice  :-)
author: Tanja
